reviews.text: Horrible service! And 魚片頭 was not 魚片頭, it was 魚Fu
always get the egg noodle with beef. never disappointed. open late. hot sauce is fire.
Wonderful and unique
Ordered won ton and beef noodle ... Won tons are cold and beef are hard ... I have never had such bad experience before

The operators haven't got heart to run the shop, in my opinion! Their signature dishes should be fish balls but tasteless and without any texture. The dumplings haven't got any sharps and taste plain. Of course no service here. Besides I saw them adding some white power in the soup. I hope that it isn't MSG.
